<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.7.9">
<l>pēyiṉār mulaiyūṇ piḷḷaiyā yorukāl perunilam viḻuṅkiya tumiḻnta</l>
<l>vāyaṉāy mālā yālilai vaḷarntu maṇimuṭi vāṉavar tamakkuc</l>
<l>cēyaṉā yaṭiyēṟ kaṇiyaṉāy vanteṉ cintaiyuḷ ventuya raṟukkum</l>
<l>āyaṉā yaṉṟu kuṉṟamoṉ ṟeṭuttā ṉaraṅkamā nakaramarn tāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who lies calmly in the great city of Araṅkam is the one who lifted</l>
<l rend="indent">the mountain one day, having become a child who fed</l>
<l rend="indent">on the demoness’ full breasts,</l>
<l>Being the one whose mouth at one time having gulped the vast earth,</l>
<l rend="indent">spewed it out, being Māl,</l>
<l>Having slept on a banyan leaf, being one who is remote</l>
<l rend="indent">to the jewel-crowned celestials, being one who is near to me, his servant,</l>
<l>Being a herder who comes and cuts away the harsh suffering in my mind.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
